Definition: a nonlethal aerosol spray made with the pepper derivative oleoresin capiscum
Example: used to cause temporary blindness and incapacitate an attacker; also used as a bear deterrent
Synonyms: aerosol, chemical_weapon, a, nonlethal, spray, made, with, the, pepper, derivative, oleoresin, capiscum, used, to, cause, temporary, blindness, and, incapacitate, an, attacker, also, as, bear, deterrent
Category: noun.artifact
